This repository provides a bridge between GPT-SoVITS and Wyoming protocol APIs.

It is built to work with these upstream open-source projects:
- GPT-SoVITS (MIT License): https://github.com/RVC-Boss/GPT-SoVITS
- Wyoming protocol/reference implementations (MIT License): https://github.com/OHF-Voice/wyoming

This project does not bundle copied source files from those repositories.
If copied code is added in future, the original license headers and notices
must be retained.
